<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA8">
<l>ukantuṉṉai vāṅki yoḷiniṟaṅkoḷ koṅkai</l>
<l>yakaṅkuḷira vuṇṇeṉṟā ḷāvi – yukantu</l>
<l>mulaiyuṇpāy pōlē muṉintuṇṭāy nīyu</l>
<l>malaipaṇpā lāṉamaiyā laṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She who joyfully inclined [her] light-coloured breast to you</l>
<l>[and] said ‘drink so as to cool [your] insides’, [acting] as if you joyfully</l>
<l>drank from [her] breast you drank [her] soul in hatred,</l>
<l>grace to your flexible nature, that day.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
